AI safety note: the Child Mode safety layer is a best-effort prompt-based
guardrail on a third-party large language model (Google Gemini). It is not
a substitute for adult supervision, and the maintainers make no guarantee
that every response will be age-appropriate. Adult supervision of any
child using this Software is recommended.
